{"tid":2177066,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"四男被控襲便衣警開審　被告：遭警掌摑、膝撞、拳打逼供招認","createTime":"2020-08-27T12:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T15:41:38.000Z","uid":56115,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7cf691a190407e2a9e483634967971b143871fa6","tid":2177066,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:46:07.000Z","msg":"今年元旦大遊行被警方腰斬後，多區發生警民衝突。其中警方在旺角展開驅散行動時，4 名男子被指在山東街與通菜街交界襲擊一名便衣男警，今（27 日）在西九龍裁判法院開審。其中一名被告今表示將會爭議招認，指警員曾在警署內掌摑、及膝撞拳打他腹部一分鐘，威迫他作出招認；又指警員是在嫲嫲回家時尾隨入屋搜查，更一度威嚇他如果保持緘默，將會禍及家人。報稱受襲的警員則供稱，當日進行便裝巡邏時想以手機拍照匯報，被一名男子喝止後遭人追打跪頸，暈倒數分鐘。審訊明續。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%83%E6%97%A6%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E5%9B%9B%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%A5%B2%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6%E9%96%8B%E5%AF%A9-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A-%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%8E%8C%E6%91%91-%E8%86%9D%E6%92%9E-%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E9%80%BC%E4%BE%9B%E6%8B%9B%E8%AA%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2597%25A6%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25AF%25A9-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258E%258C%25E6%2591%2591-%25E8%2586%259D%25E6%2592%259E-%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%2580%25BC%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%25AA%258D%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONpa4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=12ab43fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2597%25A6%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25AF%25A9-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258E%258C%25E6%2591%2591-%25E8%2586%259D%25E6%2592%259E-%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%2580%25BC%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6